      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: var(--zy-color-primary-light);"><path d="M15 22v-4a4.8 4.8 0 0 0-1-3.5c3 0 6-2 6-5.5.08-1.25-.27-2.48-1-3.5.28-1.15.28-2.35 0-3.5 0 0-1 0-3 1.5-2.64-.5-5.36-.5-8 0C6 2 5 2 5 2c-.3 1.15-.3 2.35 0 3.5A5.403 5.403 0 0 0 4 9c0 3.5 3 5.5 6 5.5-.39.49-.68 1.05-.85 1.65-.17.6-.22 1.23-.15 1.85v4"/><path d="M9 18c-4.51 2-5-2-7-2"/></svg>
      <span>ZhouYing0818</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://zhouying0818.github.io/zying_blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--zy-space-2); font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); text-decoration: none; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); transition: color var(--zy-transition-base);" aria-label="Blog">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: var(--zy-color-primary-light);"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
      <span data-zh="个人博客" data-en="Personal Blog">个人博客</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=sn0ZCR4AAAAJ" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--zy-space-2); font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); text-decoration: none; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); transition: color var(--zy-transition-base);" aria-label="Google Scholar">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: var(--zy-color-primary-light);"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
      <span data-zh="谷歌学术" data-en="Google Scholar">谷歌学术</span>
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Ying-Zhou-257" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--zy-space-2); font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); text-decoration: none; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); transition: color var(--zy-transition-base);" aria-label="ResearchGate">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color: var(--zy-color-primary-light);"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
      <span>ResearchGate</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <!-- Brief Introduction -->
  <section class="fade-in" style="padding-top: var(--zy-space-16); padding-bottom: var(--zy-space-16);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--zy-font-display); font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 32px); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--zy-text-primary); text-wrap: balance; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-8);" data-zh="个人简介" data-en="Introduction">个人简介</h2>
    <blockquote style="position: relative; padding-left: var(--zy-space-5); padding-top: var(--zy-space-1); margin: 0; border-left: 3px solid var(--zy-color-accent); color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.75;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: var(--zy-text-base); font-style: italic;" data-zh="致力于将计算生物学应用于生物医学研究领域。在复旦大学期间，通过整合计算与实验方法研究中间神经元分类与脑回发育，深化了对神经发育及电生理数据分析的理解。随后的临床研究经历激发了我对优化基因变异解读计算方法的兴趣，而在哈尔滨医科大学的深造则进一步提升了我利用生物信息学方法探索脑肿瘤与神经干细胞关联的能力。熟练掌握多组学数据分析（包括sc/snRNA-seq、ChIP-seq、WES/WGS等），能运用统计学习与生物信息学流程处理从电生理信号到测序的多种生物数据。" data-en="Eager to apply computational expertise to advance biomedical research. At Fudan University, employed integrated computational and experimental approaches to investigate interneuron classification and gyrus development. Clinical research inspired development of computational methods for variant interpretation. Training at Harbin Medical University advanced computational skills in exploring links between brain tumors and neural stem cells. Highly proficient in multi-omics data analysis including sc/snRNA-seq, ChIP-seq, and WES/WGS.">致力于将计算生物学应用于生物医学研究领域。在复旦大学期间，通过整合计算与实验方法研究中间神经元分类与脑回发育，深化了对神经发育及电生理数据分析的理解。随后的临床研究经历激发了我对优化基因变异解读计算方法的兴趣，而在哈尔滨医科大学的深造则进一步提升了我利用生物信息学方法探索脑肿瘤与神经干细胞关联的能力。熟练掌握多组学数据分析（包括sc/snRNA-seq、ChIP-seq、WES/WGS等），能运用统计学习与生物信息学流程处理从电生理信号到测序的多种生物数据。</p>
    </blockquote>
  </section>

  <!-- Education Timeline -->
  <section class="fade-in" style="padding-top: var(--zy-space-16); padding-bottom: var(--zy-space-16); border-top: 1px solid var(--zy-border-subtle);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--zy-font-display); font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 32px); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--zy-text-primary); text-wrap: balance; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-8);" data-zh="教育经历" data-en="Education">教育经历</h2>
    <div class="zy-timeline">
      <!-- Timeline Item 1 -->
      <div class="zy-timeline-item">
        <div class="zy-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
          <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-base); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary); font-family: var(--zy-font-body);" data-zh="硕士 | 哈尔滨医科大学，生物医学工程（生物信息学方向）" data-en="MS | Harbin Medical University, Biomedical Engineering (Bioinformatics)">硕士 | 哈尔滨医科大学，生物医学工程（生物信息学方向）</h3>
            <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2022.09 - 2025.06</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin-top: var(--zy-space-1); color: var(--zy-text-secondary);" data-zh="GPA 3.8，研究方向：scRNA-seq、ChIP-seq、CUT&RUN|TAG、Ribo-seq、AS|APA、CRISPR Screens等" data-en="GPA 3.8, Focus: scRNA-seq, ChIP-seq, CUT&RUN|TAG, Ribo-seq, AS|APA, CRISPR Screens">GPA 3.8，研究方向：scRNA-seq、ChIP-seq、CUT&amp;RUN|TAG、Ribo-seq、AS|APA、CRISPR Screens等</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Timeline Item 2 -->
      <div class="zy-timeline-item">
        <div class="zy-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
          <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-base); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary); font-family: var(--zy-font-body);" data-zh="硕士 | 复旦大学，神经生物学（神经发育与神经元分类）" data-en="MS | Fudan University, Neurobiology (Neurodevelopment & Neural Classification)">硕士 | 复旦大学，神经生物学（神经发育与神经元分类）</h3>
            <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2016.09 - 2020.01</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin-top: var(--zy-space-1); color: var(--zy-text-secondary);" data-zh="论文答辩 92.32/100分，GPA 2.99/4.0" data-en="Thesis defense 92.32/100, GPA 2.99/4.0">论文答辩 92.32/100分，GPA 2.99/4.0</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Timeline Item 3 -->
      <div class="zy-timeline-item">
        <div class="zy-timeline-dot"></div>
        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
          <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1);">
            <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-base); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary); font-family: var(--zy-font-body);" data-zh="学士 | 湖南农业大学，生物工程" data-en="BS | Hunan Agricultural University, Bioengineering">学士 | 湖南农业大学，生物工程</h3>
            <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2012.09 - 2016.06</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin-top: var(--zy-space-1); color: var(--zy-text-secondary);" data-zh="GPA 3.59/4.0" data-en="GPA 3.59/4.0">GPA 3.59/4.0</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Research Projects -->
  <section class="fade-in" style="padding-top: var(--zy-space-16); padding-bottom: var(--zy-space-16); border-top: 1px solid var(--zy-border-subtle);">
    <h2 style="font-family: var(--zy-font-display); font-size: clamp(22px, 2.4vw, 32px); font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.2; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--zy-text-primary); text-wrap: balance; word-break: keep-all; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-8);" data-zh="项目经历" data-en="Projects">项目经历</h2>
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--zy-space-5);">

      <!-- Project 1 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="胶质母细胞瘤（GBM）与神经发育轨迹的系统比较" data-en="Systematic comparison of GBM and neurodevelopmental trajectories">胶质母细胞瘤（GBM）与神经发育轨迹的系统比较</h3>
          <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2023.01 - 2025.06</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;" data-zh="整合分析了5个GBM单细胞/单核转录组数据集，将数据与胎儿发育轨迹进行比对，系统描绘了GBM中动态变化的分子表达谱" data-en="Integrated 5 GBM sc/snRNA-seq datasets, aligned with fetal developmental trajectories to profile dynamic molecular expressions in GBM">整合分析了5个GBM单细胞/单核转录组数据集，将数据与胎儿发育轨迹进行比对，系统描绘了GBM中动态变化的分子表达谱</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); margin-top: var(--zy-space-2); color: var(--zy-text-muted);" data-zh="哈尔滨医科大学" data-en="Harbin Medical University">哈尔滨医科大学</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 2 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="基于bulk与单细胞RNA测序及机器学习发现骨关节炎诊断性生物标志物" data-en="Discovery of Diagnostic OA Biomarkers via bulk and scRNA-seq and ML">基于bulk与单细胞RNA测序及机器学习发现骨关节炎诊断性生物标志物</h3>
          <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2025.07 - 2026.11</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;" data-zh="整合bulk与单细胞RNA-seq数据，利用机器学习方法鉴定骨关节炎诊断的5基因生物标志物组合" data-en="Integrating bulk and scRNA-seq data to identify a diagnostic 5-gene biomarker panel for osteoarthritis using ML">整合bulk与单细胞RNA-seq数据，利用机器学习方法鉴定骨关节炎诊断的5基因生物标志物组合</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); margin-top: var(--zy-space-2); color: var(--zy-text-muted);" data-zh="自由职业生物信息工程师" data-en="Freelance Bioinformatician">自由职业生物信息工程师</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 3 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="探索非酒精性脂肪肝中配体-受体相关基因的潜在关系" data-en="Ligand-receptor related genes in NAFLD">探索非酒精性脂肪肝中配体-受体相关基因的潜在关系</h3>
          <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2025.07 - 2026.11</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;" data-zh="结合bulk与单细胞RNA-seq数据，利用机器学习与计算药物发现方法，鉴定NAFLD中配体-受体互作相关生物标志物" data-en="Combining multi-omics with computational drug discovery to identify ligand-receptor biomarkers in NAFLD">结合bulk与单细胞RNA-seq数据，利用机器学习与计算药物发现方法，鉴定NAFLD中配体-受体互作相关生物标志物</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); margin-top: var(--zy-space-2); color: var(--zy-text-muted);" data-zh="自由职业生物信息工程师" data-en="Freelance Bioinformatician">自由职业生物信息工程师</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 4 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="通过熵加权集成多种工具改进外显子组分析中的变异优先级排序（共同第一作者，已发表）" data-en="Improving variant prioritization by entropy-weighted ensemble (First co-author, published)">通过熵加权集成多种工具改进外显子组分析中的变异优先级排序（共同第一作者，已发表）</h3>
          <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2020.05 - 2022.10</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;" data-zh="在大型罕见病队列中对多种变异优先级排序工具进行基准测试，采用熵加权集成方法优化变异优先级排序" data-en="Benchmarking variant prioritization tools in a large rare disease cohort, using entropy-weighted ensemble to improve prioritization">在大型罕见病队列中对多种变异优先级排序工具进行基准测试，采用熵加权集成方法优化变异优先级排序</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); margin-top: var(--zy-space-2); color: var(--zy-text-muted);" data-zh="上海交通大学医学院附属新华医院" data-en="Xinhua Hospital, Shanghai Jiao Tong University School of Medicine">上海交通大学医学院附属新华医院</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 5 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="Sncg、Mybpc1和Parm1对体感皮层VIP阳性中间神经元亚群的分类（已发表）" data-en="Sncg, Mybpc1, Parm1 classify VIP interneuron subpopulations (Published)">Sncg、Mybpc1和Parm1对体感皮层VIP阳性中间神经元亚群的分类（已发表）</h3>
          <span style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); font-weight: var(--zy-font-medium); white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0; color: var(--zy-color-accent); font-family: var(--zy-font-mono);">2017 - 2020.05</span>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-secondary); line-height: 1.7; font-style: italic;" data-zh="应用无监督学习和机器学习方法分析高维形态学与电生理数据，构建定量特征提取方法分类VIP+中间神经元亚群" data-en="Applied unsupervised and ML methods to analyze high-dimensional morphological and electrophysiological data for VIP+ interneuron classification">应用无监督学习和机器学习方法分析高维形态学与电生理数据，构建定量特征提取方法分类VIP+中间神经元亚群</p>
        <p style="font-size: var(--zy-text-xs); margin-top: var(--zy-space-2); color: var(--zy-text-muted);" data-zh="复旦大学" data-en="Fudan University">复旦大学</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Project 6 -->
      <div class="project-card">
        <div style="display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: baseline; justify-content: space-between; gap: var(--zy-space-1); margin-bottom: var(--zy-space-3);">
          <h3 style="font-size: var(--zy-text-sm); font-weight: var(--zy-font-semibold); margin: 0; color: var(--zy-text-primary);" data-zh="断奶后隔离对C57BL/6J小鼠焦虑和抑郁样行为的影响（已发表）" data-en="Effect of post-weaning isolation on anxiety/depressive-like behaviors in C57BL/6J mice (Published)">断奶后隔离对C57BL/6J小鼠焦虑和抑郁样行为的影响（已发表）</h3>
